name: Static_minusTest
description: Unit tests for the Static.minus method, which removes all occurrences of a specified element from a list.

test_cases.name: testMinus_AllElementsRemoved
test_cases.description: Tests the Static.minus method when all occurrences of the specified element are removed from the list.

test_cases.name: testMinus_NoElementsRemoved
test_cases.description: Tests the Static.minus method when no elements are removed from the list because the specified element is not present.

test_cases.name: testMinus_EmptyList
test_cases.description: Tests the Static.minus method when the input list is empty.
